body:
Despite what doujins tell you biology usually doesnt allow two completely different species to breed. So the scientist's plan makes more sense. Let the elves breed with each other and then brainwash their children.
That being said, no reason for the succubus to be left out. I am looking forward to her getting some of Amelia as well. And with the author saying he wants a happy ending I think this will turn out alright.

@D4rknessza The orc is not involved in any of the sex. He is just there for exposition, so he isnt relevant to the actual tags.
